ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMuskowekwan Indian Reserve No. 85-62, No. 85-64 ** SETTING APART ** LED-09-03
PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the MUSKOWEKWAN BAND, of 64.75 hectares (160 acres) of surface land, excluding mines and minerals, situated in the Rural Municipality of Kellross No. 247, near the Village of Leross, Saskatchewan, as Muskowekwan Indian Reserve No. 85-62 and 129.5 hectares (320 acres) of surface land, exlcuding mines and minerals, situated in the Rural Municipality of Emerald No. 277, near the Village of Wishart, Saskatchewan, as Muskowekwan Indian Reserve No. 85-64.
